Description:
   Compact Amplification is a passive arcane refinement technique unique to
   the Magi. Through intensive study of magical compression, the Magi learns
   to compact more raw power into each spell without increasing its mana cost.
   The technique involves folding magical resonance back into the casting
   matrix, amplifying the output of every spell cast.

   This passive skill increases the potency of the Magi's spells, effectively
   raising their magical supremacy when this technique is mastered. It stacks
   with other magical enhancement abilities. The Magi becomes capable of
   achieving spell outputs that exceed what their raw mana pool would normally
   allow, making each point of mana invested more efficient.
